title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Oh Hello - Ra Ra Riot and Delicate Steve
description:
Check out this Oh, Hello featuring Ra Ra Riot and Delicate Steve as they talk about recording a Limited Edition Split 7" in celebration of Record Store Day. The vinyl is only available on 5/20/12 at participating stores. Only 500 hand numbered copies on white vinyl with art by the Silent Giants.

Side A: Ra Ra Riot with Delicate Steve - Valerie 
Side B: Delicate Steve with Ra Ra Riot - The Big Ship 

Delicate Steve's sophomore release Positive Force will be released on July 10th through Luaka Bop.
To find out more about Rubber Tracks visit:
www.converse.com/rubbertracks
